snippet.textDisplay: What a musical journey! Thought it was a Kannada song, but during Navratri, it revealed itself as Gujarati. "Gothilla" in Kannada means "don't know," adding to the surprise. In Gujarat, it's a quest to "find him/her." India's cultural diversity in a song - truly incredible. 🥰
snippet.textOriginal: What a musical journey! Thought it was a Kannada song, but during Navratri, it revealed itself as Gujarati. "Gothilla" in Kannada means "don't know," adding to the surprise. In Gujarat, it's a quest to "find him/her." India's cultural diversity in a song - truly incredible. 🥰
